dct_description_sm: New Jersey Deparment of Conservation and Economic Development. Division of Planning and Development. Atlas Sheet 37 (1952) New Jersey Geological Survey. Alternate title: [New Jersey.] Atlas sheet no. 37. Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depths are shown by soundings in feet at mean or half tide. Title was not given. Region covered: Cape May County. Original survey made under direction of C. C. Vermeule, Topographer in 1880-3; 1952 revision by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1952.
